rawContent:
'''''The Desert Trout''''' was the ship of [[Taiman]] and his crew from [[Al Kharid]]. It was a fishing boat and sailed out from Al Kharid every fortnight to fish. However not long ago, the ship was attacked by [[Tempoross]], an ancient sea spirit. The ship was sunk by the powerful storm Tempoross whipped up. Taiman and his crew all survived and washed ashore near Al Kharid, where they reported the event to [[Chancellor Hassan]], who called upon help from more fishers to fight against [[Tempoross]].

The crew of ''The Desert Trout'' consisted of four members: [[Taiman]] the skipper, [[Koanee]] the navigator, [[Timallus]] the chef and [[Lauretta]].
